T1  - Has the Euro Paid Off? A Study of the Trade-Induced Welfare Effects of the EMU
AU  - Esteve-Pérez, Silviano
AU  - Gil-Pareja, Salvador
AU  - Llorca-Vivero, Rafael
AU  - Paniagua, Jordi
